en_160417_0	A child of a group of children who went for bathing in a stream has gone missing in Helagampura in Damana.
en_160417_1	Police said that the group has been bathing in the afternoon yesterday when one kid has been driven away by the waves.
en_160417_2	The missing child is a 16 year-old school student.
en_160417_3	Meanwhile, a youth has gone missing when bathing in Kothmale Oya in Dimbulapane area.
